Unit Name: Flotilla
Author: The Martian
Released: Jun 23 2020


This archive contains 8 sprite sheets of 2x2 units for use with OpenXcom.

4 of them have a stationary body the other 4 have a hovering animation.

You will need to use drawingRoutine: 12 (Hallucinoid) for them to animate correctly.

Images created by Duke_Falcon were used to make the Flotilla so please credit him as well if you choose to make use of this unit in your project.
